  -n, --dry-run         Show what would happen, make no changes
  -v, --verbose         Verbose output
  -V, --version         Show version

Environment:
  RECIPES_DIR    Recipes directory
  OUTPUT_DIR     Output directory
  GPG_KEY        GPG key ID
  AUTO_PUSH=1    Auto-push after generate
